{"tid":634465,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【有對話截圖】賭波貼士網大小通吃　女學生數百元都呃","createTime":"2018-04-19T08:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T09:45:33.000Z","uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cc405a2e7c9fe241268f4a948a5bcd73539b234c","tid":634465,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由過去揚言「做人做狗自己決定」，到今日轉攻女網民揚言「幫姊妹發達」，社交平台賭波貼士網騙案，禁之不絕。本報再接到數宗投訴，事主損失由幾百至數千元不等。有個案事主自言，誤信貼士網聲稱「命中率」高達九成，轉帳「入會」後收到假料，投注未中過，要求退錢又不果，血本無歸。<br />\n<br />\n有事主稱，看到社交平台上有組織聲稱可以幫人賺錢，見平台上貼出不少「贏錢經驗」，遂查詢會費及每場貼士收費等。對方聲稱貼士準確率高達九成，若計劃不達標，可以退回費用；又強調戶口有齊姓名和地址等資料，絕不「走數」。事主信以為真，轉帳2500元加入「5日計劃」，之後連續幾天根據報料投注，一場也沒中過。到他要求退錢時，對方再沒回應。<br />\n<br />\n另有平台以女網民為主要目標，多則facebook帖文聲稱，可以幫到女士「7日袋走20萬」、「過闊太生活」、「日日買新手袋」等。有女學生稱曾查詢入會事宜，支付500元以為可以「玩一星期」，對方卻稱她只是付了500元本金，不是會費；如要收到「貼士」，最低消費一個月，須另加6000元。事主以「無錢玩住」為由要求退回本金，由上月中多番追討到上星期，忽然收到一場「貼士」並稱「500一場計劃已完結」，之後平台再無回訊。<br />\n<br />\n她說，有關facebook專頁每日都會公布贏了多少錢，但是對比過對方提供資料，根本所謂「貼士」與最終結果完全不一致，認為平台是靠電腦後製加工，製作贏錢假象騙取網民信任。事主希望透過分享自己經歷，呼籲其他朋友和市民不要上當。<br />\n<br />\n類似騙財手法大約在2014年起出現。多個平台手法類似，都是貼出主持人贏大錢，然後聲稱可以提供貼士助人致富。有事主到銀行入錢時，即使銀行職員提醒「近日有多筆金錢存入同一戶口」，仍沒為意照樣過數。另外上當失財的不止本地人，在警方公布個案中，曾有台灣人誤信騙徒有準確賭波貼士「出售」，先後存入了22萬港元到指定戶口。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a0d7f805e7ba46355637c3d8cb2d3884.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa0d7f805e7ba46355637c3d8cb2d3884.jpg&h=40a61603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a2439e4f02bd36df9409b023d92792b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa2439e4f02bd36df9409b023d92792b7.jpg&h=69c461f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a0db82ffe4fa4090515ce064036a4b8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa0db82ffe4fa4090515ce064036a4b8e.jpg&h=66fe49cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a0dc67cafac1b62899fe4b7506bb4531.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa0dc67cafac1b62899fe4b7506bb4531.jpg&h=acd36b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a0dd8438aa195ba23aa4659481b9ec3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa0dd8438aa195ba23aa4659481b9ec3d.jpg&h=bad351e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a0deab80ebd390fa99de59888c0747b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa0deab80ebd390fa99de59888c0747b5.jpg&h=b9e12850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a0dfeba3f3110d2abc890d1b6084f422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa0dfeba3f3110d2abc890d1b6084f422.jpg&h=9af0949c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a0e0b7d4dfc95def05619f761d794e95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa0e0b7d4dfc95def05619f761d794e95.jpg&h=f6542eca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58b45e7e8efd1199bcde5cdda007de75feeb4c2a","tid":634465,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deeeb6ff5b22c7d04f22591a0e0d84ab09fa415e","tid":634465,"uid":169555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:04:13.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"4970a543ba7877bbbcf4c3e31701104da20adc06","tid":634465,"uid":16881,"like":3,"dislike"